sium, gabapentin, levetiracetam, and paracetamol. Its active pharmaceutical ingredients are used for the treatment of anti-inflammatory, analgesic and antipyretic, anti-diabetic, anti- platelet, anti-cholesterol, anti- convulsant, anti-epileptic, anti-hypertensive, and anti-cholelithic, as well as proton pump inhibitor. IOL Chemicals and Pharmaceuticals Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Ludhiana, India."}}